messages.message:
Hi all! (cc <!subteam^SPYBRCK6X>)

At @Aaron Vontell's request, here is a document that we can use to coordinate Summer Intern 2020 Matchmaking.

Let's all use this to list:
1. Candidates we're pursuing
2. Desire to be a mentor
3. Potential projects we can offer interns as a "menu" for those that do not have a clear project pre-identified going in.
If such a list already exists, let me know and I'll merge any info in this document over!

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RcUOPcJ4abCQ84CMPu4f5FQaDtIjf_jNlqnyOqiRNa8/edit#heading=h.5hitjeoacts2
I think @Felicia / @Erick brought up the idea for mentor-mentee matching :slightly_smiling_face: thanks for creating this!
